{"tid":1165584,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"我敢肯撚定，屎為個鴻懵OS會採用以下方法推出","createTime":"2019-05-22T01:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T17:00:53.000Z","uid":80650,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"36966892da998f867d945250a2bab8b2019fbc2e","tid":1165584,"uid":80650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"1. 系統核心一定大量抄襲android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 介面應該極為接近而家既屎為an機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 會有自己app store<br />\n4. 外銷版本(即非大陸版)個app store會將所有/絕大部分google play store上面既常用app偷放上去<br />\n5. 會有齊google app，例如gmail、 google map、youtube、google drive、翻譯等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. 雖然個系統核心無辦法直接link到GMS，但其他google app可以正常運行，類似ios上面既google app咁<br />\n7. 其實最接近既例子係之前Blackberry BBOS試行android app咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a23c014a960704685bcae0ba003adce44344ede","tid":1165584,"uid":130901,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"廢話"},{"pid":"0f56181c210dfa206ef5a67558894851bf955e93","tid":1165584,"uid":112416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"問題係，點解我唔買其他牌子呢？"},{"pid":"388a1f139a8b663eb48630a4bab3241926efd64f","tid":1165584,"uid":91631,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"夠擔抄既 google實告佢<br />\n<br />\n大陸就無佢辦法姐 大陸以外就係人地地頭"},{"pid":"bffea0d76b75ba2ff185bec8e8e054197900fbff","tid":1165584,"uid":249473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f135ea9fe0d322515d84e06e650093719af44049","tid":1165584,"uid":62011,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"紅芯瀏覽事件翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6b7fe3636fad0b93f290c98b3080d1680eb7